HEADWORD: Aizoaceae
<hw>Aizoaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a natural family of succulent
herbs or small shrubs mostly of South Africa but also New Zealand and
North America: carpetweeds; fig marigolds.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Aizoaceae</fam>,
<fam>Tetragoniaceae</fam>, family <fam>Tetragoniaceae</fam>, carpetweed
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
